1. *Piješ* li kafu svako jutro? (Are you drinking coffee every morning?)
2. *Pitao* sam te da li ideš na žurku večeras. (I asked you if you're going to the party tonight.)
3. Ja *pijem* čaj umesto kafe. (I'm drinking tea instead of coffee.)
4. Oni *piju* vino svake večeri. (They drink wine every evening.)
5. Da li ti *prijatelji piju* alkohol? (Do your friends drink alcohol?)
6. *Pitom* pas je bio veoma poslušan. (The tame dog was very obedient.)
7. Moram da *napijem* biljke u bašti. (I have to water the plants in the garden.)
8. *Piću* se služe na zabavama i skupovima. (Drinks are served at parties and gatherings.)
9. *Pitanje* je bilo vrlo teško za odgovoriti. (The question was very difficult to answer.)
10. Možeš li mi *dopustiti da popijem* čašu vode? (Can you allow me to have a glass of water?)